{"tid":332033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車路士小將倒米侮辱中國 球迷要官方道歉","createTime":"2017-07-22T16:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T00:50:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e67a314e6741b39a189b59330491e4430dd05be5","tid":332033,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"車路士喺周六(22日)晚上於中國鳥巢同阿仙奴踢熱身賽，但陣中巴西小將羅拔堅尼地喺instrgram上載兩條影片，其中一條寫住「Porra China」，「Porra」係葡萄牙文粗口。另一條就上傳一個保安靠喺門前好似瞌著咗，並加咗一句「Acorda China」，即「醒醒，中國」。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起軒然大波，雖然羅拔堅尼地其後刪除影片並且公開道歉，但唔少球迷仍然非常不滿，仲話會抵制羅拔堅尼地一切活動，要車路士官方一個道歉或交待。車仔嚟中國踢熱身賽就係要宣傳球會，開拓市場做生意，羅拔堅尼地今次真係倒米，睇嚟呢次真係手尾長囉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170722/photo/bkn-20170722191131186-0722_00882_001_01p.jpg?20170722191141\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170722191131186-0722_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20170722191141&h=37fd075c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170722/photo/bkn-20170722191131186-0722_00882_001_02b.jpg?20170722191141\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170722%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170722191131186-0722_00882_001_02b.jpg%3F20170722191141&h=8307fbd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c7daa614f17af0627355d9db8410ebc5f819bb0","tid":332033,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"搞下笑都唔得<br />\n<br />\n中國人真係 D幽默感都無"},{"pid":"3bee9935e0a6f2cf9738364ffb38d3923316f1ba","tid":332033,"uid":16034,"like":13,"dislike":5,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搞下笑都唔得<br />\n<br />\n中國人真係 D幽默感都無</blockquote><br />\n都係得香港會咩都屌柒自己友先者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係人都知呢d亞洲之旅係用黎掠水架啦仲搞串個party"},{"pid":"255657508cbd3ebcc28f7de5aaa8c72bd0ffc1de","tid":332033,"uid":23848,"like":30,"dislike":4,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0